data.description: This well loved home has had 2 owners and is bigger than it looks! It has a nice sized add-on for entertaining or relaxing.  It boasts 1 level living, new windows, new garage door, updated bath and carpet and a Nuvo water softener system. Roof is about 8 years old. Home has an extra driveway & basement entrance.  This home will need some updating, its' being sold" AS IS"   Seller has a home warranty in place through Elevate Homescriptions, the Totally Elevated Plan.  No showings before 11 am.  Dotloop Ok, please attach a PDF.  While all listing details and square footage are deemed reliable, buyer to verify  all.
